INTERACTING WITH THE PARTICLE SYSTEM

Try modifying the sketch by completing some of these tasks.

Change the particle size
Modify the size variable so particles become bigger or smaller.

Change the particle speed
Adjust the movement by changing the values multiplied with cos(angle) and sin(angle).

Change the number of particles
Increase or decrease the number created in setup().

Change the particle color
Modify the fill() color inside the display() method.

Change the trail effect
Adjust the transparency in:

fill(0, 20);

Smaller numbers create longer trails.

Change the movement pattern
Modify the noise scale:

noise(x * 0.005, y * 0.005, noiseOffset)

Try values like 0.002, 0.01, or 0.02.

Add mouse interaction
Create new particles at the mouse position when clicking.

Example idea:

particles.add(new Particle(mouseX, mouseY));

Experiment
Try combining multiple changes and observe how the visual behaviour evolves.